OL,3,CAndy Burnham confirms he would run in
OL,4,Crace to replace Keir Starmer
OL,6,FAndy Burnham has said he would
OL,7,Fchallenge Sir Keir Starmer if he wins
OL,8,Fthe Makerfield by-election and a
OL,9,Fleadership race to replace the prime
OL,10,Fminister was triggered.
OL,12,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor has
OL,13,Fpreviously promised a vote for him in
OL,14,FMakerfield would be a vote to "change
OL,15,FLabour", but has not explicitly said
OL,16,Fhe would launch a bid until now.
OL,18,FHe is widely viewed as Starmer's main
OL,19,Frival for the top job if he wins.
OL,26,@vD@_OUwD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
