OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780697476
OL,3,CAndy Burnham confirms he would run in
OL,4,Crace to replace Keir Starmer
OL,6,FAppearing on the BBC's Question Time
OL,7,Fby-election special, he said he had
OL,8,Fasked his team to help "develop a
OL,9,Fpolicy" but will need the backing of
OL,10,Fthe Parliamentary Labour Party.
OL,12,F"I'm not somebody who gets ahead of
OL,13,Fmyself. I can't do anything unless I'm
OL,14,Flucky enough to get the support of
OL,15,Fpeople here," he said.
OL,17,F"But if I get your support, I would
OL,18,Fseek to represent you at the highest
OL,19,Fpossible level and give this
OL,20,Fconstituency maximum power and
OL,21,Finfluence.
OL,26,@pD@XOUqD@GO]tD@AOUwD@MO]yD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
