PN,31403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780697476
OL,3,CAndy Burnham confirms he would run in
OL,4,Crace to replace Keir Starmer
OL,6,F"I think Wes Streeting seems to have
OL,7,Flaunched a leadership contest, so if
OL,8,Fthat is running, I would seek to join
OL,9,Fit. But I'd have to persuade members
OL,10,Fof the Parliamentary Labour Party to
OL,11,Fdo the same."
OL,13,FIn just over two weeks, Makerfield ` a
OL,14,Fcentury-long Labour stronghold - will
OL,15,Fvote on whether Burnham should return
OL,16,Fto Parliament and mount his challenge.
OL,18,FThe stakes are high, with Makerfield
OL,19,Frecently swinging heavily in favour of
OL,20,FReform in the local elections.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
