OL,3,CAndy Burnham confirms he would run in
OL,4,Crace to replace Keir Starmer
OL,6,FReform is hoping to beat Burnham and
OL,7,Fembarrass both him and the Labour
OL,8,FParty.
OL,10,FThe Conservative candidate in the by-
OL,11,Felection, Michael Winstanley, said he
OL,12,Fwas "disgusted" by Burnham's decision
OL,13,Fto trigger the by-election.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
