PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780697476
OL,3,CAndy Burnham confirms he would run in
OL,4,Crace to replace Keir Starmer
OL,6,FSpeaking on the same episode of
OL,7,FQuestion Time, he pointed out that it
OL,8,Fwas not long ago that Burnham was
OL,9,Fsaying being the mayor of Greater
OL,10,FManchester was the "greatest job in
OL,11,Fthe world" and said, "I'm actually
OL,12,Fquite disgusted, really, and sad that
OL,13,Fwe're having this by-election foisted
OL,14,Fupon us."
OL,16,FThe by-election was triggered when
OL,17,Fformer Starmer ally Josh Simmons
OL,18,Fresigned his seat, specifically
OL,19,Fendorsing Burnham to replace him.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
