OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1780697476
OL,3,CAndy Burnham confirms he would run in
OL,4,Crace to replace Keir Starmer
OL,6,FStarmer has insisted he will continue
OL,7,Fin his role as prime minister and has
OL,8,Fsuggested he would fight any
OL,9,Fleadership challenge.
OL,11,FUnder Labour Party rules, the
OL,12,Fincumbent leader is automatically on
OL,13,Fthe ballot if they wish to be.
OL,15,FThere has never been a leadership
OL,16,Fchallenge to a leader of the Labour
OL,17,FParty while they are the prime
OL,18,Fminister.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
